  <p class=MsoNormal  style="text-indent:21.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count:2.0000; text-align:left; line-height:150%; " ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:Arial; mso-hansi-font-family:Arial; mso-bidi-font-family:Arial; font-size:10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt; " >基础债权清偿期届满之日，基础债权债务人无力归还借款本息，则甲方应当自行及时将借款本息支付给丙方，并委托丙方在收到借款本息后的两个工作日内向乙方支付债权</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-family:Arial; font-size:10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt; " >收益权</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:Arial; mso-hansi-font-family:Arial; mso-bidi-font-family:Arial; font-size:10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt; " >本息，回购债权</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-family:Arial; font-size:10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt; " >收益权</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:Arial; mso-hansi-font-family:Arial; mso-bidi-font-family:Arial; font-size:10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt; " >。丙方代甲方向乙方支付债权</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-family:Arial; font-size:10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt; " >收益权</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:Arial; mso-hansi-font-family:Arial; mso-bidi-font-family:Arial; font-size:10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt; " >本息之日，乙方在本协议项下购买的债权</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-family:Arial; font-size:10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt; " >收益权</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:Arial; mso-hansi-font-family:Arial; mso-bidi-font-family:Arial; font-size:10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt; " >转归甲方所有。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:Arial; mso-hansi-font-family:Arial; mso-bidi-font-family:Arial; font-size:10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt; " >
